Och det med brittisk accent till och med! Men samtidigt som Walter återfinner sig sjalv tar hans nya baverpersonlighet snart over helt!

programme.title: The Happytime Murders

Phils gamla tjej (spelad av Elisabeth Banks) har utsatts for hot och ar nasta tilltankta offer. Snart pekar misstankarna mot Phil sjalv. Han sticker och måste nu ensam forsoka losa The happytime murders.

Den faktaorienterade neuroforskaren Julias forskning om hur den kvinnliga och den manliga hjarnan fungerar illustreras med hjalp av tre olika par i olika faser i deras forhållanden. programme.desc: 7 Days to Vegas is an edgy comedy that is based on a true story of the rise and fall of one of Hollywoods biggest poker games. The names have been changed to protect the guilty. Out of desperation to feed his family, Duke Hamilton, a washed up Hollywood actor in the 90s, starts up a small poker game from his house in the lower-class part of the San Fernando Valley. With the help of his wife KC, the game grows to attract some of the biggest players in the Los Angeles area. These risk-taking guys, who will bet on anything, live life on the edge. Its not just Poker that these spoiled LA moguls bet on.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: The Girl Next Door
programme.desc: Matthew Kidman (Emile Hirsch), en vanlig kille som går sista året på gymnasiet, blir kar i den nyinflyttade grannen Danielle (Elisha Cuthbert från TV-serien “24”), en sexig och snygg tjej som tycks ha allt. Snart får han veta att hon ar en mycket speciell tjej - Danielle har ett forflutet som fore detta porrstjarna. Matthew riskerar allt och får uppleva saker aldrig kunnat forestalla sig...

programme.title: Uptown Girls
programme.desc: Brittany Murphy och Dakota Fanning lyser starkare an alla ljusen i Manhattan i denna underbara New York-saga. Molly (Murphy) ar en festglad prinsessa vars pengar precis tagit slut. Ray (Fanning) ar en kravande nioårig flicka vars senaste barnflicka precis slutat. Nar Rays alltfor upptagna mamma (Heather Locklear) anstaller Molly som Rays nya barnflicka ar det den perfekta chansen for båda flickorna att andra sina vanor och upptacka att ibland kan din basta van komma i den mest ovantade formen!

programme.title: Balls Out: Gary the Tennis Coach
programme.desc: En overentusiastisk vaktmastare på en high-school I USA ger sig på att trana ett gang missanpassade ungdomar for att vinna Nebraska state tennis championship.

programme.title: Wagons East
programme.desc: De kom for guld, men nu nojer de sig med rinnande vatten. John Candy och Richard Lewis spelar huvudrollerna i denna dråpligt okonventionella blick på den legendariska vastvarlden.

programme.title: Big Mommas: Sådan far sådan son
programme.desc: Martin Lawrence i komedirollen som Big Momma, en skojfrisk tant från Sodern med mangder av tokiga tricks i bakfi ckan. Efter att ha bevittnat ett mord går FBI-agenten Turner (Lawrence) och hans styvson undercover på en fl ickskola for blivande artister.

programme.title: Dom kallar mej Trinity - Djavulens hogra hand
programme.desc: Denna vildsinta parodi på ""7 vågade livet"" gjorde Spencer/Hill till stjarnor! Han har en kaft lika valoljad som hans revolver. Han har ett rykte lika smutsigt som kladerna han rider i. Han sager att han ar en fredens man - men vem vågar tro honom? Hans namn ar Trinity - Djavulens hogra hand. I stan traffar Trinity sin ohangde bror Bambino och de kommer i bråk med den skurkaktige Majoren som forsoker ta over stan. Men Trinity och Bambino moter hotet med det enda språk som bovar forstår kulor och storsmockor!

programme.title: Trinity klipper till igen
programme.desc: Men hor och hapna: Nu har de slagit sig på en karriar som hemliga poliser, med uppdrag att satta fast ett storsmugglande banditgang. For bra for att vara sant? Ja faktiskt, for de ar sjalva ute efter att håva in formogenheten. Och for att vinna guld kommer de offra mycket bly.Men till skillnad från andra vilda fighter och skottdueller finns har många vinnare. Vapentillverkare, bandageforsaljare och dodgravare till exempel. Och framforallt lakarna som måste ta hand om alla som skrattat kakarna ur led! Terence Hill and Bud Spencer ar ett av filmhistoriens popularaste hjaltepar, som dunkat skurkar ihop I nitton filmer!

programme.title: Barbershop
programme.desc: Ice Cube, Anthony Anderson, Sean Patrick Thomas, Eve och Cedric the Entertainer spelar huvudrollerna i denna hysteriskt roliga komedi om en barbershop i Chicago dar knivskarp humor aldrig går ur tiden! Calvin (Ice Cube) ar en blivande entreprenor med stora planer... och att driva sin familjs barbershop ar inte en av dem. Men nar han impulsivt saljer butiken till en skum lånehaj inser han snart hur viktig kvartersalongen ar for honom... och hur långt han ar beredd att gå for att få tillbaka den!

programme.title: The Rules of Attraction - Lustans lagar
programme.desc: Jessica Biel, James Van Der Beek och Ian Somerhalder ger liv och skratt till den har arliga och skarpsinniga betraktelsen på sociala och sexuella forhållanden på college.

programme.title: Next Day Air
programme.desc: Nar en chauffor på villovagar av misstag levererar ett paket som innehåller kokain till fel adress, satter det igång en desperat jakt på kokainet mellan den ursinnige langaren som har skickat det, de skrackslagna avsedda mottagarna som missade det, och de konspirerande oavsiktliga mottagarna som planerar att ta det.

programme.title: Thanks for Sharing
programme.desc: Adam (Mark Ruffalo) har just firat 5-årsdagen som "nykter" sexmissbrukare, då han moter Phoebe (Gwyneth Paltrow) som han inleder en haftig flirt med. I terapigruppen for sexmissbrukare traffas också frisoren Dede (Pink) och norden Neil (Josh Gad) men det ar inte helt enkelt att vara van med någon av det motsatta konet nar sex har odelagt alla ens tidigare relationer.

programme.title: Låt de doda vila
programme.desc: Jimmy ar inte bara en fan av heavy metal, skrack, och det ockulta. Han har ett mål: han vill kontakta sin avlidna mamma. Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: Fighting Caravans
programme.desc: Clint Belmet (Gary Cooper) is a frontier scout with his hands full in this 1931 Paramount Pictures version of Zane Greys novel. Hes helping guide a wagon train across the country, fighting off various attacks on the way, and falling for his lovely Felice (Lily Damita). Belmets grizzled companions think he should leave the woman alone, but it gets lonely out on the trail, and Felices charms are hard to resist. Featuring such notable character actors of the period as Ernest Torrence, Tully Marshall, and Fred Kolher, this vintage Hollywood Western still packs a wallop!

programme.title: American Empire
programme.desc: This epic of Americas westward march stars Leo Carrillo and Preston Foster in a tale of men building a cattle empire, only to battle rustlers, the weather, and each other! The romantic adventure from director William C. McGann (In Old California, Alcatraz Island) features a strong leading performance by Oscar nominated RKO star Richard Dix (Cimarron, The Ghost Ship) plus cinematography by six-time Oscar nominee Russell Harlan (To Kill a Mockingbird, Rio Bravo).

programme.title: Valley of Vengeance
programme.desc: LUST FOR GOLD BROUGHT MASSACRE TO HUNDREDS! Death Rode the Plains! Directed by Sam Newfield and starring Buster Crabbe (Flash Gordon) and Al St. John, Valley of Vengeance opens with Billy Carson (Crabbe) shooting two affluential town officials after they - and a band of outlaws - had murdered his and Fuzzys (St. John) parents years earlier. Arrested for the shootings, Billy tells the story of the outlaws killing his parents and the events that led to his shooting the town officials. Will Billy be able to prove his innocence and bring and end to the corrupted officials?

programme.title: Red Ryder: Roll, Thunder, Roll!
programme.desc: Red Ryder finds two silver conchas, the trademark of bandit El Conejo, at a raided ranch. He reports the raid to Marshal Bill Faugh but tells him that he suspects that El Conejo, a Robin Hood type character, is being framed.

programme.title: The Two Gun Man
programme.desc: Ken Maynard stars in this vintage western about ranchers under threat from hired gunmen. Director Phil Rosen, whose career dated back to working with Thomas Edison and included several Charlie Chan features, keeps the action hot with help from a strong ensemble, including Charles King, Murdock MacQuarrie, and a horse named Tarzan! Maynard plays Blackie Weed, a marshall going undercover to capture and arrest some cattle rustlers.He finds himself up against some very bad men, and hes soon framed for murder. Watch as Blackie blazes his way to vindication with a .45 in either hand and the flame of righteous anger in his eyes... Kitty: Nita Martin. Joe Kearney: Lafe McKee. Lem Tolliver: Tom...

programme.title: Springtime in the Sierras
programme.desc: Ads for this Roy Rogers classic roared HEAD FOR THE MUSICAL HILLS...ROY IS GUNNIN FOR THRILLS! And thrills are what youll get when you watch this fun, action packed B-Western from Republic Pictures. Theres some great comic relief from Andy Devine and Chester Conklin, two of Hollywoods all-time greats. This old-fashioned shoot-em-up was directed by William Witney, who would go on to direct many of televisions top western sagas, including Bonanza, Wagon Train, and The Wild, Wild West.

programme.title: Diamond Trail
programme.desc: Diamond Trail is an epic that starts in the speeding taxicabs and illegal barrooms of the east coast, and travels west for its exciting climax. Reporter Speed Morgan (Rex Bell), going undercover as Frisco Eddy, infiltrates Flash Barretts gang in order to bring them all to justice. But can he get the job done before they learn his identity? With a cast that includes Frances Rich and Bud Osborne, this action tale from director Harry L. Fraser (The Last of the Clintons) is another forgotten classic from Monogram Pictures.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney take time out from their duties to try and collect the bounty posted on a legendary golden wolf that roams the Colorado foothills. A couple of wolf hunters dont take kindly to a pair of amateur hunters horning in on their range and attempt to drive the G-Men away before they can capture or kill their quarry.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney travel to Wyoming to oversee a land opening and end up playing nursemaid to a pair of identical twin pranksters and a kooky Chinese cook. Meanwhile, a trio of outlaws are pursuing the twins seeking information they possess. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Uncle Joe tries to advertise Shady Rest as a hotel for honeymooners.But is Hooterville really the best place for a honeymoon? Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E13 A Night at the Hooterville Hilton
programme.desc: Upon reading a fantastical brochure Uncle Joe made, a hotel critic comes to Shady Rest. Can Hooterville live up to Joes hype? Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho work to uncover a cattle rustling operation.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog..The show was nominated for a PrimeTime Emmy Award in 1951. This episode aired in 1950. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho investigate when a railway detective is found dead.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Frank and Jesse James
programme.desc: Detective Matt Clark tracks down the James Brothers who seek revenge on the law following the death of their half-brother.This western adventure series earned a Primetime Emmy in 1955.. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle. Directed by William Witney. Episode first aired in 1954. Also, look for legendary tough guy actor lee Van Cleef as Jesse James.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Railroad detective Matt Clark is challenged by a band of freight-car robbers led by Apache chief Geronimo. This western adventure series earned a Primetime Emmy in 1955.. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle, plus Chief Yowlachie and Emile Meyer. Directed by William Witney.Produced by B movie veteran Edward J. White. Episode first aired in 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: While attempting to steal land from an Indian tribe, crooked ranchers kill one of the braves. The Judge must move fast to prevent an all-out massacre. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In Family Ties, Judge Bean comes to the aid of the Peralta family as unscrupulous real estate agents try to force them off their land. Theyve learned that a railroad will need the property and they intend to make an undeserved profit. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Sam is framed by Duke and his gang, who have kidnapped Linda to prevent Sam from proving his innocence. Its up to Annie and Lofty to save Sam from an angry mob, save Linda from Duke and his gang, and take them down for their crimes. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Annies younger brother finds himself in danger when he gets in trouble with The Shadow Gang after running away with a friend. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This entertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook suspect that Carpenter is being bamboozled by the Mohawk guide helping him establish a new settlement. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Tensions rise when a Tuscarawas man tries to incite war against the settlers. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.sub-title: S01 : E22 Blood on the Land
programme.desc: Adam Cartwright finds himself hostage to Jeb, a dangerous sheep herder who wants Ben to sign over a large plot of land.Starring Michael Landon as Little Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Wildfire: The Story of a Horse
programme.desc: Fanning (John Miljan) has his men rustle horses and then blame it on a wild horse named Wildfire. Happy and Alkali arrive and immediately get into trouble with Fanning and his men. When Alkali is shot, Happy catches the outlaws but the Judge not only releases them, he discharges the Sheriff and tries to arrest Happy for rustling! Starring Bob Steele and Sterling Holloway, directed by Robert Emmett Tansey. 1945 (Color).

programme.title: Grand Canyon Trail
programme.desc: Roy Rogers and Trigger star in this Republic Pictures feature about the hunt for silver in a deserted ghost town. Songs include Colorado Joe and Everythings Going My Way. Plus, look for Andy Devine as Cookie Bullfincher. Film buffs should look for silent screen foil James Finlayson, a familiar face from various Keystone Cop comedies, as the local sheriff.

programme.title: Jesse James Rides Again
programme.desc: The outlaw Jesse James and his friend are on the run from the law when he is wrongly accused of leading the historic 1876 Northfield, Minnesota bank robbery. With nerve-tensing turns and high-impact action, Jesse rides into a town where a gang is trying to drive area ranchers off their land because theres oil underneath it. Jesse James takes particular interest in the situation of a pretty young woman and her elderly father, whose ranch is being regularly attacked by the gang.

programme.title: The Star Packer
programme.desc: He Dared Death In The Outlaws Lair! John Travers (John Wayne) takes on a mysterious gang leader known as The Shadow in this vintage western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Director/writer Robert N. Bradbury (Blue Steel, Riders of Destiny) gets the best of a remarkable cast that includes George Gabby Hayes. Of interest to film buffs is that the feature was shot in various California locations by Oscar winning cinematographer Archie Stout (The Quiet Man).

programme.title: Raiders of Red Gap
programme.desc: Bobs Playin A Mystery Hand... Hes Marked For Death By Killer Bullets As Gunfire Echoes Over The Plains! After one of his ranch hands is killed when a gang attacks his ranch, Jim Roberts joins forces with his neighbor in an effort to fight off the Bennett Cattle Co., a company looking to rob them of their land. Things get increasingly dangerous as the company hires Butch Crane, a professional killer, to stop them. Directed by Sam Newfield (Racing Luck (1935), Go-Get-Em, Haines (1936)), Raiders of Red Gap stars Robert Livingston (The Three Mesquiteers (1936), Larceny on the Air (1937)) as Rocky (Lone Rider) Cameron and Al St. John (Billy the Kid Trapped (1942), Border Feud (1947)) as...

programme.title: The Sundowners
programme.desc: Brother battles brother in this gritty tale of feuding ranchers in the old west. This story of the Texas panhandle stars such familiar faces as Robert Preston, Chill Wills, and Jack Elam, and was a rare film for its time in that it was filmed almost entirely in Texas with no studio interiors. If for no other reason, watch this one for Prestons performance. If you only know him from The Music Man or Victor Victoria, youre sure to be surprised here! (also, look for John Drew Barrymore as Jef Cloud. He was part of the famous Barrymore family, and father of Drew Barrymore.) Jim Strake: Frank Cordell. The Whip: Dave Kashner. Directed by George Templeton

programme.title: Courageous Avenger
programme.desc: Gold, gangs, and the heroic fight for life! Johnny Mack Brown (Billy the Kid, Coquette) stars in this western thriller about murders going on in a mining community. Its a story full of twists, where the greed for gold is only surpassed by the struggle for life!

programme.title: Born to Battle
programme.desc: Cyclone Tom Saunders starts a ruckus in a Chinese laundry and has to go before a judge. Unable to pay his fine, he is bailed out by a local cattle rancher and agrees to do 30 days work for him. Its not too long before he becomes enmeshed in a war between rustlers and outlaws.

programme.title: Brothers of the West
programme.desc: Tom Tyler plays Tom Wade, a range detective whose brother has been accused of robbery and murder. Wade has only one clue to prove his brothers innocence: a set of unusual tire tracks. This film was directed by Sam Katzman, who later became known as Jungle Sam for his association with a variety of jungle thrillers, and then as a master of all exploitation genres, from teen horror to flying saucer flicks!

programme.title: Sitting Bull
programme.desc: A cavalry officer sympathetic to the wronged Sioux tribe fixes a meeting between Chief Sitting Bull and President Grant but a dishonest Indian Agent and a hateful General Custer test the Siouxs patience, threatening to derail the peace-talks. Directed and co-written by Sidney Salkow; starring Dale Robertson, Mary Murphy, J. Carrol Naish. Also, look for legendary character actor Iron Eyes Cody as Crazy Horse.

programme.title: Neath Canadian Skies
programme.desc: Its the mounties versus claim jumpers in this drama from Golden Gate Pictures. Based on an action-packed novel by James Oliver Curwood and directed by B. Reeves Maynard (Undersea Kingdom, The Phantom Empire), the film features an outstanding cast of Poverty Row regulars, including Russell Hayden, Inez Cooper, Cliff Nazarro, I. Stanford Jolley, and Kermit Maynard. For movie buffs: Cinematographer Marcel Le Picard began his career in the silent era and finished with exactly 200 credits!

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Ben helps three deserters, escaped from an Army stockade. Learning what they had to deal with, Ben promises to share the truth with his friend who is in charge of the fort.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Ben and Adam are in jail, about to be hung for a crime they didnt commit. Joe and Hoss must find out why the witnesses to the alleged crime have lied about what happened before the execution takes place. They receive help from a vagrant named Lassiter who is looking for the men who committed a lynching in Kansas years ago.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: The son of a neighboring rancher intends to sell their land for a mining operation that will ruin the water rights agreement that Andy and Ben made years ago. Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: The Cartwrights take a young boy to the Ponderosa after the death of his mother. Hoss is the only one that is able to get through the boys hostility and bitterness, but, as the two begin to get close, the boys father breaks out of prison and comes to retrieve the boy.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Little Joe Cartwright tries to help a gypsy girl who was abandoned by her people - because they believed she was a werewolf.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: After Farmer Perkins murders a store clerk in front of his wife, and is allowed to walk after his trial, the Cartwrights step in to make sure hell be rearrested, tried, and hung.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Homer Bedloe (Charles Lane) threatens to close down the Cannonball on Christmas Eve, disrupting the Shady Rest hotels holiday plans. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Directed by Guy Scarpita. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: When Herby (Don Washbrook) gets drafted, Kate tries to cheer him up by saying he could become an astronaut. Could hooterville actually send someone ito the space program? Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E16 Bobbie Jo and the Beatnik
programme.desc: Bobbie Jo falls head over heals for an edgy young poet from New York. He likes her, too, but hes not fond of Hooterville. Of coure, Kate has to show Bobby Jo what this pompous fool is all about. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963. Look for Dennis Hopper as the beatnik.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E17 My Daughter the Doctor
programme.desc: The family wants Billie Jo to become a doctor, but she wants to go to Hollywood to become an actress. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough. And be sure to look for Adam West in a pre-Batman role as Doctor Clayton Harris. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in January, 1964.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Billie Jo recieves an endowment, but instead of using it for medical school, she wishes to go to Hollywood.Kate meets with Judge Drucker to see if she can legally prevent the girl from goinng. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E19 Visit from a Big Star
programme.desc: A famous movie star (John Vivyan) stays at the Shady Rest Hotel. He wants to get away from the spotlight for a while, but it appears that Uncle Joe has told the entire valley that the hotel has a special guest. .Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Ralph Levy. Episode first aired January 28, 1964

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Uncle Joe tries to convince two rich women that Shady Rest is a farm. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Guy Scarpitta..Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aried in February of 1964.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E21 The Very Old Antique
programme.desc: Homer Bedloe (Charles Lane) tries to sell the Cannonball to a rich man as an antique.Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1964.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Spur Line to Shady Rest
programme.desc: The Shady Rest hotel is threatened when a railroad detective comes to investigate a forgotten spur line on the property. Creator Paul Henning followed up the success of The Beverly Hillbillies with this charming CBS comedy that ran for 222 episodes. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Quick Hide the Railroad
programme.desc: Kate uses her charms to keep Homer Bedloe from catching the train to Pixley. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Bedloe: Charles Lane. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Custers Last Stand
programme.desc: The survivor of an Indian attack acquires a rare medicine arrow, and a menacing character named Blade (Reed Howes) will stop at nothing to take it from him. Elmer Clifton (Assassin of Youth, Seven Doors to Death) directs a memorable cast that includes Rex Lease (The Sign of the Wolf, The Monster Walks), Lona Andre (Slaves in Bondage, Death in the Air), and William Farnum (Samson and Delilah). Meanwhile, Frank McGlynn Jr is in the title role of General George A. Custer.

programme.title: Enemy of the Law
programme.desc: Tex Ritter stars in this western drama about a man who goes undercover to befriend a convict believed to have stolen a shipment of government gold. Also starring Guy Wilkerson as Panhandle Perkins, this offering from Hollywoods Poverty Row features the usual fistfights and entertaining storyline that made these modestly budgeted features well worth watching. Songs include Teach Me To Forget and You Will Have to Pay both sung by Tex!

programme.title: Lawless Frontier
programme.desc: John Wayne stars in this vintage western about a man avenging the murder of his parents. Other cast members include frequent Wayne sidekick George Gabby Hayes, plus Yakima Canutt, Sheila Terry, and Jack Rockwell. This Paul Malvern Production from director Robert N. Bradbury also features Earl Dwire, one of the great B-movie villains, as Zanti, the ruthless bandit who sets the action in motion.

programme.title: Adventures of Gallant Bess
programme.desc: Rather than a gorgeous Hollywood starlet, actor Cameron Mitchell (Carousel), playing cowboy Ted Daniels, shares the screen in this film with a magnificent wild horse named Gallant Bess, who he tames, trains and keeps for himself. But after Ted is gravely injured in a fixed rodeo, Bess is stolen away from him and forced to join a cruel traveling carnival in this fast-paced western from director Lew Landers (The Adventures of Rin Tin Tin).

programme.title: The Kansan
programme.desc: Richard Dix stars in this epic of the boisterous and brawling Old West! Wounded in a gun battle with the notorious James gang, John Bonniwell (Dix) wakes up in the hospital to find out hes been elected marshal! He quickly learns that this hot-headed frontier town can only be cooled off with blazing lead and dynamite! Jane Wyatt, Albert Dekker, Victor Jory, and Robert Armstrong also star in this tale of smashing fists and crashing bullets from director George Archainbaud (The Lost Squadron).

programme.title: The Fighting Westerner
programme.desc: A mining engineer tries to solve the murders of several heirs to a valuable radium mine in this western drama from Paramount Pictures. Stars include Charles Chic Sale, and in one of his early roles, Randolph Scott. This feature, also known as Rocky Mountain Mystery, was directed by Oscar winner Charles Barton, who would go on to direct several popular television shows, including Petticoat Junction and Family Affair...

programme.title: Projekt Z
programme.desc: En grupp filmstudenter tar med sig tre lediga skådespelare till ett nedlagt hotell i de norska fjallen for att spela in en zombiefilm. Deras fiktion blir plotsligt verklighet nar en okand varelse borjar terrorisera filminspelningen.

programme.title: Calamari Union
programme.desc: Sjutton unga man, varav sexton heter Frank och bar svarta glasogon, lamnar en elandig arbetarmiljo och beger sig ut på en farlig resa genom storstaden på jakt efter den mytiska stadsdelen Eira. På grund av olika omstandigheter kommer bara två av dem fram. Men Eira ar inte riktigt det de hoppats på och deras sokande fortsatter – nu i en roddbåt mot Estland… Denna surrealistiska komedi ar Kaurismakis andra långfilm. En skon och absurd berattelse som blandar amerikansk gangsterfilm med finsk punk.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: Mannen utan minne
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om en man som tappar sitt minne och får hjalp av fattiga men storhjartade manniskor i en containerby.

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Del 2
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg ar en storslagen film om Klemens (Peter Stormare) och hans systerson Nejla som lever mitt i det norrlandska landskapet på gransen mellan Sverige och Norge.

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Brott och straff
programme.desc: En filmatisering av Dostojevskijs roman med samma namn, som utspelar sig i 1980-talets Finland. Romanen Brott och straff ar ansedd som en av vår tids storsta litterara verk. Fjodor Dostojevskij målar upp det moraliska dilemmat huruvida ett brott, i det har fallet ett mord ar forsvarbart om resultatet blir positivt for många, om andamålet helgar medlen. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Så olika
programme.desc: Så olika ar en komedi om karlek. Det kretsar kring två systrar, den ena nytillsatt finansborgarråd i Stockholm, nyskild och mamma till två dottrar. Den andra en sjalvstandig TV-producent som har fått i uppdrag att gora ett nytt direktsant sångprogram från Skansen - nu mitt bland djuren! Den handlar om att bli sanslost foralskad i sin varsta fiende, om manniskor som mots trots att de ar fundamentalt olika. For har overvinner karleken allt - från politisk maktkamp till dans med salarna på Skansen.

programme.title: Den Svavelgula Himlen
programme.desc: Forfattaren Frej blev i tonåren kar i overklasstjejen Stella Rabell. Deras starka band overlevde mot alla odds det stormiga forhållandet under decennierna som foljde. Nar Stellas storebror Alex blir knivhuggen borjar Frej tanka tillbaka till saker som har hant från det lyckliga 70-talet och framåt.

programme.title: Kommissarie Spack
programme.desc: Kommissarie Mårten Spack har kallats till en brottsplats dar en kropp hittats genomborrade med knivar, gafflar, skedar och en hogaffel. Till allas forvåning drar Kommissarie Spack slutsatsen att det ror sig om ett sjalvmord. Spack ser kopplingar till andra sjalvmord och konstaterar att kåren fått en galen seriesjalvmordare på halsen. Han kommer snart på andra tankar nar hans råbarkade kollega Grunvald Karlsson hittar andra spår  något som leder till något storre an vad de kunnat ana. En ny kollega, superpolisen Irene Snusk kopplas in på fallet. Tillsammans ska trion losa ett av de viktigaste fallen i svensk kriminalhistoria.

programme.title: Projekt Z
programme.desc: En grupp filmstudenter tar med sig tre lediga skådespelare till ett nedlagt hotell i de norska fjallen for att spela in en zombiefilm. Deras fiktion blir plotsligt verklighet nar en okand varelse borjar terrorisera filminspelningen.

programme.title: Lindell - Sorgmanteln - Del 2
programme.desc: Fyra små flickor på ett fotografi. Tjugo år senare hittas en av dem mordad. En annan ar spårlost forsvunnen. Cato Isaksen ar redo att losa nya kriminalgåtor. Lise Sommer blir upphunnen av sitt forflutna. Hennes basta van Esther Synnøve Lønn har hittats mordad med avskuren hals. Några dagar senare forsvinner Esthers son. Nar polisen borjar att skrapa på ytan visar det sig att en barndomsvan till Lise och Esther Synnøve också saknas. Forhållandet mellan vaninnorna doljer morka understrommar. Vad var det egentligen som hande nar flickorna var små? Och deras mammor - vad doljer de?

programme.title: Låt de doda vila
programme.desc: Jimmy ar inte bara en fan av heavy metal, skrack, och det ockulta. Han har ett mål: han vill kontakta sin avlidna mamma. Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: Lindell - Orkestergraven - Del 1
programme.desc: Efter sitt livs basta forestallning på Operan blir forstaviolinisten Siv Ellen Blad brutalt mordad. Kriminalkommissarie Cato Isaksen får snart veta att hon har utsatts for ett postrån. Finns det ett samband?

programme.title: Zombie och spoktåget
programme.desc: Zombie (Silu Seppala: Leningrad Cowboys) ar en individ som går sin egen vag och inte kan folja de normer som det finska samhallet har satt for honom. Zombie beslutar sig for att lamna allt och ge sig utomlands - till en plats dar ingen forvantar sig något av honom. Zombie och spoktåget betraktas av många som några av Mika Kaurismakis basta filmer. Filmen belonades med Jussi-priset for Basta regissor, Basta manliga huvudroll och Basta foto år 1992. Tragikomiskt och aven surrealistiskt foljer Zombie med bland andra Mato Valtonen och Sakke Jarvenpaa från Sleepy Sleepers, samt naturligtvis Matti Pellonpaa.

programme.title: Amazon
programme.desc: Den finske mannen Kari (Kari Vaananen) bestemmer seg for å flytte til Brasil med sine to døtre etter kona hans dør. Snart møter han den eventyrlystne amerikanske flygeren Dan (Robert Davi: Die Hard), som forteller Kari om planen sin om å grave etter gull i Amazonas-jungelen. Men Kari møter også den vakre Paola (Rae Dawn Chong: Commando), som lærer ham mer om situasjonen i Amazonas og truslene mot den.

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: Klanen - berattelsen om Grudornas slakt
programme.desc: "Klanen" ar historien om en brottslig slakt dar Mika Kaurismaki behandlar existensens villkor genom den traditionella episka formen, på gransen mellan ratt och fel i lagen. Alexander, den yngsta sonen, ar slaktens vita får. Han forvantas hålla sig på den raka vagen, till skillnad från sin far och andra man i slakten. Men familjen ar varst, och blod ar tjockare an vatten... Familjedramat "Klanen" ar en storslagen hyllning till den gamla finska filmen.

programme.title: De arvlosa
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaens forsta långfilm. Han skrev manuset tillsammans med sin bror Aki. "De arvlosa" ar en tidlos skildring av hur småskurken Manne, bonddrangen Harri och den vackra Veera kor en Volga genom de forsvinnande finlandska landskapen, med poliser och gangsters standigt på halarna. Den fartfyllda resan ackompanjeras av tidlosa låtar av bland annat Juice och Rauli Badding.

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Part 1
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Del 2
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Pax
programme.desc: En flygmotor exploderar, och planet stortar mot marken. Mycket tyder på att detta ar slutet for alla ombord. Men for några av dem ar det en ny borjan. I luften mellan Stockholm och Oslo foljer vi sju personer och ett hjarta på vag från en kropp till en annan. Nar den tunga maskinen faller ser de livet i ett annat ljus. Aldrig ar livet så narvarande som nar slutet narmar sig. I detta storslagna, romantiska och nargångna dramas ensemble finns flera av Sveriges mest namnkunniga skådespelare, bland annat Samuel Froler, Thomas von Bromssen, Bjorn Granath, Annika Hallin och Marika Lagercrantz.

programme.title: Låt de doda vila
programme.desc: Jimmy ar inte bara en fan av heavy metal, skrack, och det ockulta. Han har ett mål: han vill kontakta sin avlidna mamma. Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.title: Lindell: Dromfångaren - Del 2
programme.desc: En olidligt spannande kriminalhistoria dar de psykologiska undertonerna bar handlingen framåt tills det hela slutar i en dramatisk kapplopning med en iskall mordare. Vem ar fonstertittaren som som står och betraktar de unga kvinnorna i lagenheten mitt emot? Har han något med mordet på nittonåriga Therese Geber att gora? Är det samma man som tar sig in i deras lagenhet på natterna? Kriminalkommissarie Cato Isaksen får ett nytt fall på halsen.

programme.title: Bleeder
programme.desc: Louise alskar Leo djupt, hjartligt och unreservedly och lyckligtvis glad nar hon upptacker hon ar gravid. Men for Leo ar den oforutsedda graviditetsfallet, Det får koppen att stromma over. Barnet betyder ett bestamt farval for hans sista, glittrande hopp att bryta ut ur den sorgliga miljon och bli något.

programme.title: 1979 Unleashed!

programme.title: Bruno Brookes UK Top 20 of the 70s
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Bruno Brookes UK Top 20 of the 70s
programme.desc: Including 10 million sellers back when it was still a rare achievement! These are the 20 biggest songs of the decade with Julie Covington, David Soul, Abba, Queen, Blondie and Wings.

programme.title: Tony Blackburns Pop Pin-Ups!
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Tony Blackburns Pop Pin-Ups!
programme.desc: Tonys pulled out quite a list of pop pinups for 2 hours of indulgence. Bolan, Bowie, Cassidy, an Osmond, Abba girls, Rod, and ladies men Barry White and Demis Roussos. Phwoar!

programme.title: Can You Keep a Secret
programme.desc: Emma sitter på ett plan som hon tror ar på vag att storta. Hon berattar darfor alla sina hemligheter for en snygg framling. Åtminstone tror hon att han ar en framling...tills hon traffar Jack, hennes foretags nya vd, som alltså vet varenda pinsam hemlighet om henne. Baserad på romanen med samma namn på New York Times bastsaljarlista, från forfattaren till ”En shopaholics bekannelser”, Sophie Kinsella.

programme.title: They Came Together
programme.desc: Nar Joel (Paul Rudd) och Molly (Amy Poehler) mottes var det hat vid forsta ogonkastet: hans storbolag Godiskompaniet hotade att stanga ner hennes bohemiska godisaffar. Plus att Joel fortfarande hade kanslor for sitt sexiga ex (Cobie Smulders). Men, trots allt så blir de kara, tills dess att de gor slut och Molly borjar dejta sin revisor (Ed Helms). Men, precis i sluttampen...tja, du får se helt enkelt. (Ledtråd: Joel håller ett stort tal och de hittar tillbaka till varandra.) Från regissoren som skapade Wet Hot American Summer, Wanderlust och Role Models kommer nu en helknapp och satirisk underminering av den romantiska komedigenren.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Broken English
programme.desc: Nora Wilder håller på att tappa hoppet. Alla i hennes narhet ar i ett forhållande, ar gifta eller har barn. Nora ar i 30-årsåldern, ensam med ett jobb hon inte trivs med och en mor som standigt tjatar om allt. Och så har vi ju hennes basta kompis Audreys "perfekta brollop". Efter flera misslyckade dater moter hon helt ovantat fransmannen Julien som har en stark passion for livet.

programme.title: Loves Last Resort
programme.desc: Efter att ha dejtat i tio år har Chloes pojkvan Eric annu ite mognat till den man hon onskar han skulle vara. Hon hoppas skynda på forloppet genom att dumpa honom. Sex månader senare traffas de och Eric avslojar nyheten om att han ska gifta sig. For att komma bort tar hon semester och på samma semesterort dyker Eric med flickvan upp.

programme.title: All For Her
programme.desc: Devina och hennes man Rick langtar efter barn. Efter år av missfall blir Devina antligen gravid. Men det visar sig att hon lider av en dodlig sjukdom. Nu borjar en kamp mot klockan, Devina måste overleva tills barnet ar fott…

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Bad Cupid
programme.desc: Archie ar en gud på uppdrag att sakerstalla så karleken alltid vinner oavsett vad. Eller åtminstone någorlunda så nar som på att man kanske dor på kuppen for den som forsoker. Egentligen så ar han inte så noga med vad resultatet blir. Hans installning som Amors forlangda arm till romantik och karlek ar snarare ratt så halvhjartad, som man bor se upp for om man hamnar i hans vag nar ska forsoker komma med en hjalpande hand. Speciellt dom som han verkligen forsoker hjalpa.

programme.title: Cooking Up Love
programme.desc: Zoey hyr en matvagn och deltar i en reality-show på TV. Det går hett till mellan henne och den stilige grundaren till snabbmatskedjan, men nar Zoey får veta att han ar domare i tavlingen, blir det frasigt i pannan. Zoey ar fast besluten om att vinna rattvist och hon misstanker att "Mr-Too-Good-To-Be-True" ar ute efter hennes såsrecept och inte hennes hjarta.

programme.title: Modern Persuasion
programme.desc: En modern version av Jane Austens roman ”Övertalning”. Wren Cosgrove ar en lycklig och framgångsrik karriarkvinna som varje kvall kommer hem till sin katt. Nar hennes firma anlitas av Owen Jasper, han som var den ratte, så vacks gamla kanslor till liv och Wren får en ny chans att uppleva den sanna karleken.

programme.title: Patrick
programme.desc: Sarah Francis ar en ung kvinna vars liv ar lite rorigt. Det sista hon behover ar någon annan att ta hand om. Ändå har hennes farmor låtit henne arva en mycket bortskamd hund, Patrick – hennes mops. Sakert hade hon en tanke bakom det? Tydligen inte, eftersom denna fyrbenta forstorare orsakar kaos på alla upptankliga satt i Sarahs liv. Men hon inser snart att Patrick ar losningen på alla hennes problem. Trots att han också ar orsaken till många av dem.

programme.title: Karlekens sloja (The Painted Veil)
programme.desc: Kitty ar en rastlos ung kvinna från overklassen som vill bort från sin familj. Nar hon traffar lakaren Walter Fane ser hon sin chans och gifter sig med honom. Tillsammans flyttar de till Shanghai dar Kitty blir foralskad i en annan man.

programme.title: If Only
programme.desc: En tragedi lar den unge engelska affarsmannen Ian Wyndham att satta karlek fore arbetet. Han lar sig antligen att oppna sig for sin sjalvstandiga flickvan Samantha Andrews.

programme.title: Albert Nobbs
programme.desc: Albert ar en forsynt man som doljer en stor hemlighet, han ar egentligen en kvinna som tvingats kla och bete sig som en man for att komma bort från fattigdom. En dag moter Albert en annan manniska i samma situation och han borjar dromma om ett liv i frihet utan hemligheter. Albert Nobbs ar en stark och rorande film med en stjarnspackad rollista.

programme.title: The Dreamers
programme.desc: Tre cineaster – den amerikanske utbytesstudenten Matthew och tvillingparet Theo och Isabelle – har kommit varandra nara genom sitt gemensamma intresse. Matthew fascineras av Theo och Isabelles oortodoxt intima band. Nar tvillingarnas foraldrar reser bort en månad bjuds Matthew in att bo hos dem, och de forlorar sig i filmisk fantasi. The Dreamers ar ett romantiskt drama av Oscarsbelonade Bernardo Bertolucci, med Michael Pitt, Louis Garrel och Eva Green i huvudrollerna.

programme.title: No Stranger Than Love
programme.desc: Vad kan vara konstigare an att ett stort hål oppnar sig i Lucy Sherringtons vardagsrumsgolv? Jo, karleken, som det visar sig.Det finns inte en man i stan som inte ar kar i Lucy. Hon ar snall, sympatisk, rolig och lojal – hon ar den perfekta tjejen som inte kan gora något fel. Ändå har hon gått med på en traff med Clint som ar gift och coach for footballaget. Precis nar de ska påborja sin affar trillar Clint ner i ett hål som oppnar sig i Lucys vardagsrum. Men det ar inte vilket hål som helst; det ar det eviga morkrets interdimensionella och enkelriktade hål. Clint fastnar nere i hålet och svavar runt i ett oandlighetens mellantillstånd.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: The Way You Look Tonight
programme.desc: Peter narmar sig 30 och ar fortfarande vilsen svulsten efter karlek med andlosa online dater utan resultat. En nyckfull date lamnar honom ensam i sangen en morgon nar han vaknar. Peter forsoker lamna allt bakom sig och fortsatter med nya dater från samma site. For varje date oppnas en helt ny varld av upplevelser och erfarenheter som får honom att ifrågasatta allt med naturkrafter, attraktion och akta karlek. Den stora frågan forblir obesvarad, kan Peter verkligen bli foralskad och hitta den akta karleken?

programme.title: Det nast basta (The Next Best Thing)
programme.desc: Yogainstruktoren Abbie och tradgårdsmastaren Robert delar det mesta i livet. Gladje. Sorg. Drommar. Och intresset for killar. Att Robert ar gay ar det enda som hindrar dem från att vara ett par. Sjalvklart festar de också tillsammans, så pass att de efter en helvild natt vaknar upp i varandras armar. De kan bara konstatera att det hant. Och att de gick for långt. På tok for långt. Beviset: ett positivt graviditetstest...

programme.title: Jack and Jill Vs. The World
programme.desc: Den framgångsrike chefen Jack (Freddie Prinze Jr.) ar en metodisk och kontrollerad man som arbetar på en ny reklambyrå på Manhattan. Under en rokpaus på kontorets hustak moter Jack skådespelerskan Jill som just anlant till New York for att soka jobb. Hon berattar om sin situation så Jack ordnar ett jobb åt henne i en reklamkampanj som hans byrå ligger bakom. Nar han sedan lamnar Jill vid hennes hem upptacker han att hon bor i ett nedgånget lågbudgethotell, så Jack erbjudar då henne att bo i hans gastrum så lange. Detta visar sig få konsekvenser som ingen kunnat ana...

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.

programme.desc: Två extremt tavlingsinriktade Super Club-anstallda tavlar om titeln "Månadens anstalld", och om att vinna den snygga nya kassorskans hjarta i denna galna komedi.

Forfattaren trodde att han skrev om framtiden, men i sjalva verket var det det forflutna. I hans roman åker ett tåg till 2046 lite då och då. Alla som åkte dit hade samma intention: att återuppleva sina forlorade minnen. Det sades att 2046 andrade sig aldrig något. Ingen visste sakert om det var sant, eftersom ingen som åkte dit någonsin hade kommit tillbaka - utom en. Han var dar. Han valde att åka darifrån. Han ville forandras.

programme.title: Very Good Girls
programme.desc: New York-tjejerna Lily och Gerry ar basta vanner på det dar viset man bara ar som ung nar man har hela livet framfor sig. De gor upp en pakt om att forlora oskulden under den sista sommaren fore collegestudierna, men denna varma sommar satts deras vanskap for forsta gången på prov nar de råkar falla for en och samma kille. En oskuldsfull tid får sitt slut på fler an ett satt.

programme.title: Don Jon
programme.desc: Don Martell ar en kille från New Jersey, vars liv kretsar kring familjen, vannerna, kyrkan – och porr. Formågan att ragga upp nya tjejer varje helg har gett honom smeknamnet ”Don Jon”. En kvall traffar han den snygga och romantiska Barbara som letar efter en underbar dromkille, en idealbild som ar valdigt långt från Don.

programme.title: L.A. Gigolo
programme.desc: Under palmerna i det solbranda Hollywood Hills njuter han av livet som player på stans trendigaste klubbar. Han traffar vackra kvinnor som kan tanka sig att låta en ”Toy Boy” bo i deras hem en kort tid i utbyte mot lite vilt och kravlost sex. Nick har koll på sitt liv och njuter av att vara uppvaktad av den framgångsrika advokaten Samantha (Anne Heche) tills han en dag traffar servitrisen Heather (Margarita Levieva) som spelar samma spel som han sjalv. Hon vill uppåt i varlden och plotsligt måste Nicki inse, att det kravs en del att ”forfora en forforare”.

programme.title: They Came Together
programme.desc: Nar Joel (Paul Rudd) och Molly (Amy Poehler) mottes var det hat vid forsta ogonkastet: hans storbolag Godiskompaniet hotade att stanga ner hennes bohemiska godisaffar. Plus att Joel fortfarande hade kanslor for sitt sexiga ex (Cobie Smulders). Men, trots allt så blir de kara, tills dess att de gor slut och Molly borjar dejta sin revisor (Ed Helms). Men, precis i sluttampen...tja, du får se helt enkelt. (Ledtråd: Joel håller ett stort tal och de hittar tillbaka till varandra.) Från regissoren som skapade Wet Hot American Summer, Wanderlust och Role Models kommer nu en helknapp och satirisk underminering av den romantiska komedigenren.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E06 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 6 - Worlds Strongest Latino
programme.desc: For the first time ever, the World’s Strongest Latino competition has begun. This two-day event in Porto, Portugal, features 20 athletes from around the world competing in 8 events. After 4 grueling events, the top 12 will advance to the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E07 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 7 - Finland World Record Breakers
programme.desc: Strongman Champions League World Record Breakers 2023 starts with a 25-ton snow plow! Crazy machines are pulled and pushed, with many kilograms moved. A few new world records are set in this competition.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E08 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 8 - Portugal
programme.desc: We have returned to the powerhouse of Portugal for an edge-of-your-seat galactic battle. If all the planets collided at once, it wouldn’t compare to the bang of this show. Get ready for the battle of the beasts; it’s the heaviest show in the universe, the Strongman Champions League.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E09 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 9 - England
programme.desc: SCL UK has landed in Gloucester it is workout war fitness for the ferocious, it’s going to be a a battle of the brutal, a rampage of the roofless. This is going to be a massacre of the muscles. You know it by now, but just in case you don’t, this is strongman champions league.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E10 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 10 - Worlds Strongest Viking
programme.desc: On the menu this week it’s medieval madness, we’ve come back to the middle ages to test our noble men through a muscle gaining of events. They are hoping and we are hoping that one will survive to take the title of the world’s strongest Viking. The official Worlds Strongest Viking is this time in Finland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: This week is a good one, can you feel the energy? Sit still, just look at me and try and feel the energy, because I can tell you, the atmosphere here is electric, it’s explosive, there is a pure elemental force going through these athletes veins. I’m shaking because it’s Poland, it’s powerful, it’s strongman champions league, and you know what Im going to say, get ready because it’s about to get heavy.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: SCL Poland part 2 - Who will win the title in Poland and take 25 points for the world ranking. It is very exciting on the top, in part 1 between Poland and Latvia. Another great episode with super strongman events such as: Bag Toss Medley, Log Lift Reps and the Powerstairs. Also an interview with Mateusz Kieloszkowski, the all time favorite champion from Poland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: It’s time to show our strength and gain respect from the gods of Olympus. Our gladiators have many events set out by no other than Hercules himself. The coliseum is ready here on this mythological island of Cyprus, so we have landed in Limassol were again 12 Top Strongmen are battling for the title and ranking points.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E14 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 14 - South Africa
programme.desc: The only and official world championship Truckpulling for its 10th year, again at the Strongman Champions league. With the 3 times Worldchampion Kelvin de Ruiter – defending his title. This championship has trucks in all shapes and sizes which is a lot like our athletes, there all different pay loads, but does the biggest win or is it the strongest.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E15 Stage 15 - SCL World Finals Bosnia
programme.desc: Years and years of determination has brought us here today, when all the walls felt like they were caving in perseverance. When their bodies were screaming, hurting, shouting stop, beneath. These are the things which make up a man, these are the things that bring you world finalists. This episode they fight for the greatest title of all, they fight to put their names in the history books forever.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E16 Stage 16 - SCL World Finals Bosnia
programme.desc: Part 2 of the World Finals of the Strongman Champions League tour 2023 at the Sarajevo Centar Skenderija in Bosnia. 3 Events was done already and amazing results have been set. Who will be the new World champion? Find out here, who, after 16 stages, will be crowned World Champion 2023.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: Across seven rivers, through mountains and forests, 12 strongmen go to toughest places to find out who is strongest Viking in the World and open a new season of Strongman champions league for 2015. Events like the Hercules Hold, Yoke Race and pulling a real Viking ship are some of the ingredients of this fantastic show.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: The second stage of Strongman champions league will be hosted in Germany, by FIBO - the leading international trade show for fitness, wellness and health worldwide with 300,000 visitors in four days. Special implements like the biggest log in the world or the special Bavarian stone lift are not only a challenge, but also an opportunity for new personal, national and world records.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 3, Holland

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 4, Finland
programme.desc: Zydrunas Savickas, one of strongest people on earth is in this competition which has attracted the attention of the audience in the battle for the title of strongest man in Finland. The next round of SCL is in Bulgaria.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 5, Bulgaria
programme.desc: The next stage of the competition is in Bulgaria where Ervin Katona (SCL World Champion 2012) will compete for the last time.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E06 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 6, Latvia
programme.desc: Krzysztof Radzikowski, the leader in the league will fight hard to keep Dainis Zageris off from the title and to gather another 25 ranking points in this next stage in Latvia.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E07 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 7, Croatia
programme.desc: The competition sees a close battle with a new world record in overhead dumbbell and close finishes throughout the day. This stage is in Croatia, in a city over 1700 years old, steeped in Roman tradition and history, the athletes arrive for the truck pull after a picturesque boat ride on the Adriatic Sea.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E08 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 8, Poland
programme.desc: We are now half way through the SCL 2015 and getting closer to the grand world finals in Turkey. The eighth stage is in Poland, the home country of the current leader Krzysztof Radzikowski.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E09 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 9, Austria
programme.desc: In this stage we go into the mountains of Austria to find out through six grueling events who is the strongest in the land of Alps. Martin Wildauer, current World Champion 2014 and Austrian local is competing alongside Zageris, Radzikowski, Belsak and many others.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E10 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 10, Romania

programme.sub-title: S02 : E11 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 11, World Log Lift Championship
programme.desc: The 11th stage is the SCL Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. In this championship, each competitor must lift three different weights overhead. Zydrunas Savickas is the current world record holder in the Log Lift.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S02 : E12 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 12, Lithuania
programme.desc: This next episode of the Strongman Champions League is hosted in Lithuania and sees us getting one step closer to the final.

programme.sub-title: S02 : E14 SCL 2015 Season 2, Episode 14, Martinique

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Julie and James are looking for a new home to raise their two boys. James is in the tech industry and would love an energy efficient home. Julie has her own dance studio and cant wait to get back to work after giving birth to her second son. Eve and Shawn are the perfect team for the job, especially with Timberworxs cutting edge "Net-Zero" project.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Kevin is a retired, successful businessman. He is a single dad to Shannon and Jennifer. Shannon has been accepted into the Ontario Veterinarian College at the University of Guelph, which is Canadas leading program in veterinary health care. This is the reason they are moving to Guelph. Kevin is happy to live anywhere as long as it has excellent golf courses. Eve will be glad to tell him that Guelph just happens to have 3 of the top ones in Ontario.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Laura is on the hunt for a new home for long time clients Marino and Paula. The couple and their three kids would like a spacious house with a country feel to escape their hectic lifestyles. Due to Marinos busy schedule as a producer, he would prefer a house that is all-inclusive and turnkey. Their kids are very active want a pool and the option for horse stables. Lauras going to find them the perfect home.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Louise, Jason, and their two children have been living in Europe for the past 10 years, but now they would like to be closer to their family in Canada. Louise absolutely adores the European aesthetic; the sense of luxury conveyed by multi-peaked roof-lines, bay-shaped windows, and decorative stone. She wants a house that allows them the feeling of "living abroad" without leaving the country.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E07 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Elizabeth and Michael are retired and want to move closer to their kids and grandchildren. They want to downsize from their two-story house into a bungalow. Luckily, Eve knows all about luxury bungalows. Elizabeth loves to exercise and really would like a gym. Michael has a passion for cars and needs at least a three-car garage. Their current house is dated so they would love a house that is turnkey. Eve will do her best to find their forever home.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Tomarra and Rob had just married and blended their two families. As a new family, they want to transition to a quiet neighbourhood away from the hustle and bustle of Toronto. Steve is up for the challenge. Rob is a writer and plans to work from home, while Tomarra is a naturopath who would love to have her own studio. Ultimately, they want to start cherishing the real things in life, and that is spending more time with their kids.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E09 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Darlene and Bruce are in the market for a new home and have enlisted Laura to help them out. Darlenes one request is that they stay close to their current home, where their daughter goes to school. For Bruce, quality construction materials and workmanship are of paramount importance. One thing the entire family agrees on is that the backyard should have a fantastic entertainment space since they spend plenty of time together outdoors and enjoy having guests over.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E10 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Kathryn and Neil are true urbanites. They love what downtown Toronto has to offer. When Neil found out his company was relocating to Guelph, they werent thrilled. After five months of long commutes, the Thompson family is ready to take the risk and make a move-with some conditions. The new house has to have a pool and playroom for the kids and a large entertainment area for adults. Eves challenge is to find them an enticing home that will convince their friends from the city to visit.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E12 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Stephanie is making a big move from BC to Guelph to be closer to her son John and his family. She doesnt want the move to be a hassle and is looking for an accessible, decent-sized home for her grandchildren and visitors from BC. Good sized guest rooms and a large backyard are a must. As she loves to cook, she would also like a new kitchen. Eve will show Stephanie 3 beautiful homes that fit the criteria. Stephanie is going to have a difficult decision.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Steve Bailey, Mike Donia and Daryl King review their favourite homes. Steve takes us down memory lane to his 18th century farmhouse, and another home with a stunning infinity pool. Daryls listings range from King city to Caloden, with helicopter pads and sprawling backyards. Mike brings us back to his fabulous listings in Thailand. He shows us a home made entirely of Bamboo, and billion-dollar property.
