programme.title: Arlington Road
programme.desc: I denna tata thriller moter vi collegeprofessorn Michael Faraday vars fru, en FBI-agent, dodats av medlemmar av en hogerextrem terroristgrupp. Nar Michael blir van med sina nya grannar, Oliver och Cheryl Lang, får han snart anledning att misstanka att något inte står ratt till. Han borjar forska i deras forflutna, men inte utan risk for sitt liv.

programme.title: A Time to Kill
programme.desc: Filmatiseringen av John Grishams bastsaljare Juryn - A Time to Kill aren stark och gripande historia regisserad av Joel Schumacher (Batman Forever, Klienten). Sandra Bullock, Samuel L. Jackson, Matthew McConaughey och Kevin Spacey spelar huvudrollerna i denna film om ett mordfall som blåser liv i rasmotsattningarna i en liten stad i Mississippi. Mitt i kaoset av marscherande aktivister, Ku Klux Klan-terror, mediahysteri och brutala upplopp forsoker en orutinerad men idealistisk ung advokat gora sig hord i sin kamp for rattvisa.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Tristan and Isolde
programme.desc: Detta ar berattelsen om engelska riddaren Tristan och den irlandska konungadottern Isolde och deras passionerade karlek till varandra, som tvingar dem att bryta alla lagar och som slutligen hotar krigsstilleståndet mellan de två landerna.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: What Maisie Knew
programme.desc: Maisie måste navigera i ett vuxen kaos med all sin oskuld, charm och villkorslosa karlek nar hon fastnar i mitten av foraldrarnas bittra vårdnadstvist. Den alltid observante Maisie kastas fram och tillbaka mellan sina foraldrar, Susanna, en åldrande rockstjarna, som jagar en sista ""hit"" och fadern Beale som ar en upptagen konsthandlare med många resdagar. Båda gifter sig med nya partners for att bli starkare i en vårdnadstvist samtidigt som Maisie knyter allt starkare band mellan sig o mammans nya pojkvan, bartendern Lincoln, inser hon att hon måste vara den vuxna i sin egen lilla familj.

programme.title: My Week With Marilyn
programme.desc: I ett desperat forsok att bli tagen på storre allvar reser ikonen Marilyn Monroe (Michelle Williams) till London 1956 for att spela mot legenden Laurence Olivier i “Prinsen och balettflickan”. Den omhetstorstande Marilyn kanner sig overgiven av maken Arthur Miller och attraherad av Oliviers assistent, den unge Colin Clark. Colin blir snart Marilyns fasta och trygga punkt, samtidigt som han också blir Oliviers endahopp att kunna slutfora sin film genom sin formåga att hålla den impulsiva Marilyn i schakt. Upp over oronen foralskadar det nu Colins hjarta som riskerar att krossas av varldens storsta och vackraste filmstjarna!

programme.title: Alvin och ganget
programme.desc: Nar misslyckade låtskrivaren Dave Seville (Jason Lee) slapper in talangfulla ekorrtrion Alvin, Simon och Theodore i sitt hem blir det musikalisk succe over en natt. Men en girig skivbolagsproducent har planer på att utnyttja ekorrganget genom att skicka dem på en lång, jobbig turne – bara for att fylla sina egna fickor.

programme.title: Hercules I New York
programme.desc: Forvisad från Mount Olympus skickas Hercules, (Arnold Schwarzenegger), till jorden dar han hittar sann karlek och borjar en lovande karriar som kroppsbyggare.

programme.title: 10 Items or Less
programme.desc: Oscar och Golden Globevinnaren Morgan Freeman spelar har en filmstjarna som ger sig ut på rollforberedande research i ett snabbkop i ostra Los Angeles. Han moter en snabbtalande kassorska (Paz Vega) och de ger sig av på en gemensam resa for att visa varandra sina respektive varldar. Strandad utan vare sig mobiltelefon eller bil accepterar han tjejens erbjudande om att ge honom lift tillbaka till Beverly Hills. Under resans gång upptacker emellertid det har till synes omaka paret att de har vissa gemensamma namnare som for all framtid kommer att forandra deras syn på deras egna liv...

programme.title: Man About Town
programme.desc: Jack Giamoro ar den amerikanska drommen forkroppsligad. Som Hollywoods mest efterfrågade talangscout tillhor han filmstadens absoluta gradda. Snabba bilar, valfyllda bankkonton och en vacker hustru - you name it, Jacks got it. Men nar han på en och samma dag forlorar sin dagbok - som ar full med konfidentiellt Hollywood-skvaller - och avslojar hustruns snedsprång, dalar Jacks tillvaro från "bling-bling" till absolut ingenting. Och så borjar guldfiskens desperata kamp for overlevnad i ett hav fullt med hajar.

programme.title: Time Out of Mind
programme.desc: George ar en desperat man. Med en vacklande halsa och ingenstans att ta vagen hamnar han på New Yorks obarmhartiga gator. Efter trostlosa forsok att hitta en tillfallig bostad tar han sin tillflykt till Bellevue Hospital, Manhattans storsta center for hemlosa man. Även har ar det en hård och tuff miljo, full av utstotta sjalar. Men nar George blir van med Dixon, en arrad hemlos man, infinner sig hoppet om att kunna reparera sitt dåliga forhållande till sin dotter.

programme.title: Halloween (Directors Cut)
programme.desc: Michael Meyers friges från mentalsjukhuset dar han var tvångsintagen i 17 år, och går barsarkagång i sokandet efter sin yngre syster. Ingen ar saker. Nyinspelning av filmen från 1978 regisserad av John Carpenter.

programme.title: Barbarian
programme.desc: Nar hon anlander till Detroit for en anstallningsintervju hyr en ung kvinna ett hus. Men nar hon anlander sent på kvallen upptacker hon att huset ar dubbelbokat och att en frammande man redan bor dar. Fast hon vet battre, bestammer hon sig for att tillbringa kvallen i hemmet, men upptacker snart att det finns mer att frukta an en ovantad husgast.

programme.title: Lost Highway
programme.desc: Fred Madison och hans fru Renee hittar mystiska videoband på verandan, på banden syns deras hus. Forst filmat utifrån. På nasta, inifrån. Polisen ar inte intresserade av att hjalpa paret, men nar annu ett videoband dyker upp och visar Renees dod vacks i stallet misstankarna mot Fred. Och darifrån ska ingenting komma att bli mindre mardromslikt. Lost Highway ar en neonoirthriller av en David Lynch i hogform, med Bill Pullman (Independence Day) och Oscarsbelonade Patricia Arquette (Boyhood) i huvudrollerna.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: The Fifth Estate
programme.desc: De borjade med att skapa en undergroundwebbplats och kom att bli varldens mest efterlysta personer. Men nar WikiLeaksgrundarnaJulian Assange och Daniel Domscheit-Berg kom over den storsta mangden sekretessbelagd underrattelseinformation som någonsin har lackt ut från det amerikanska forsvarsministeriet borjade en intern kamp. For vad ar priset for den fria varldens storsta hemligheter? Och vad kommer det att kosta att avsloja dem?

programme.title: What Maisie Knew
programme.desc: Maisie måste navigera i ett vuxen kaos med all sin oskuld, charm och villkorslosa karlek nar hon fastnar i mitten av foraldrarnas bittra vårdnadstvist. Den alltid observante Maisie kastas fram och tillbaka mellan sina foraldrar, Susanna, en åldrande rockstjarna, som jagar en sista ""hit"" och fadern Beale som ar en upptagen konsthandlare med många resdagar. Båda gifter sig med nya partners for att bli starkare i en vårdnadstvist samtidigt som Maisie knyter allt starkare band mellan sig o mammans nya pojkvan, bartendern Lincoln, inser hon att hon måste vara den vuxna i sin egen lilla familj.

programme.title: Underligare an fiktion
programme.desc: En IRS-revisor finner sig plotsligt foremål for berattande som bara han kan hora: berattande som borjar påverka hela hans liv; från hans arbete; till hans karleksintresse; till sin dod.

programme.title: In Time
programme.desc: I en framtid dar tid ar bokstavligen pengar och åldrande stannar vid 25 år, ar det enda sattet att hålla sig vid liv att tjana, stjala eller arva mer tid. Kommer Salas att leva minut till minut, tills en tidsfall ger honom tillgång till den rika varlden, dar han lagar sig med en vacker ung arvtagare for att forstora det korrupta systemet.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Tristan and Isolde
programme.desc: Detta ar berattelsen om engelska riddaren Tristan och den irlandska konungadottern Isolde och deras passionerade karlek till varandra, som tvingar dem att bryta alla lagar och som slutligen hotar krigsstilleståndet mellan de två landerna.

programme.title: This is England
programme.desc: Filmen utspelar sig i 80-talets England nar fler soldater skickas till Falklandskriget och nationalistiska krafter får fotfaste hos en arbetarklass utan arbete. Detta ar också tiden nar Ska och Oi-punk-kulturens gangbildningar snart blir uppdelade i musikfanatiker vs. skinnskallar. Mittemellan hamnar den 12-årige Shaun, som finner gemenskap i uniformen och brodraskapet som skinnhuvudena erbjuder.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: Train to Busan
programme.desc: Ett oidentifierat virus slår till mot Korea och regeringen forklarar undantagstillstånd. Staden Busan har avvarjt virusutbrottet - och de på tåget från Seoul måste nu kampa for sin egen overlevnad.

programme.title: A Bronx Tale
programme.desc: 9-årige Calogero bor i ett italienskt kvarter i Bronx. En dag bevittnar han ett mord som begås av den lokale maffiabossen Sonny. Calogero valjer att inte tjalla på Sonny, och som tack blir Sonny hans extrapappa. Calogeros hederlige far kan dock inte acceptera att sonen fostras till en gangster.

programme.title: Arlington Road
programme.desc: I denna tata thriller moter vi collegeprofessorn Michael Faraday vars fru, en FBI-agent, dodats av medlemmar av en hogerextrem terroristgrupp. Nar Michael blir van med sina nya grannar, Oliver och Cheryl Lang, får han snart anledning att misstanka att något inte står ratt till. Han borjar forska i deras forflutna, men inte utan risk for sitt liv.

programme.desc: From trying Orange zest beer and traditional Dutch dishes to exploring St.Martins Cathedral, Dom Tower and enjoying go karting and stand up paddle boat ride, watch Alex enjoy his trip in Utrecht.

programme.title: Backpack Serbia

programme.title: Boarding Pass
programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 Boarding Pass Ruka Kuusamo, Finland
programme.desc: Emeline goes to Ruka-Kuusamo, where she tries river rafting. She also meets a reindeer herder,who tells her about the unique ways of herding reindeer.

programme.title: Xplore Bhutan
programme.desc: Actress and travel enthusiast, Radhika Bangia explores the enigma that is Bhutan, when she visits Thimpu, the capital city with no traffic lights and no skyscrapers invading the skyline. Here, she checks out significant sights such as the Tibetan-style National Memorial Chorten, the National Library and the Folk Heritage Museum in order to understand more about the beliefs, history, architecture and cuisine of Bhutan.

programme.title: World Heritage

programme.desc: Explore the ancient heritage sites of Abu Simbel, the Philae complex of Nubia and the Hatshepsut Temple to unravel the mystical stories behind the ancient temples of Egypt.

programme.title: Food Fact Fun

programme.desc: Alex tries traditional Dutch food in Leiden, learns about Dutch history at Prinsenhof Museum, visits a Gothic church, a local cheese market and Delftware factory at Gouda.

programme.title: 10 Days Scotland

programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 With Love From Mauritius Ep 1
programme.desc: Krisann and Nathan’s vacation in Mauritius begins in Le Morne, where an unexpected adventure awaits the latter.

programme.title: Xplore Bhutan
programme.desc: Known as Druk Yul or the “Land of the Thunder Dragon”, Bhutan is the country of mountains, monasteries and mystery. Radhika Bangia finds this to be true when she visits Punakha, the former capital of Bhutan, where she marvels at the architecture of Punakha Dzong and gets to know the story behind the two rivers, Mo Chhu and Po Chhu. She also explores the sacred temples and Mebar Tsho lake of Bumthang, the religious heart of Bhutan, and gets to know the local legends.

programme.title: World Spas

programme.desc: Jamie Srubis tries out spa treatments, which are inspired by the Dead Sea and the desert surroundings at Hotel Kempinski Ishtar in Jordan.

programme.desc: Nestled in the mighty Alps, tour the Austrian city of Innsbruck with Sabrina and explore a town that’s alpine-urban yet traditional in nature.

programme.desc: Indeya explores the Cinnamon plantations, tries a local dish and witnesses a traditional dance performance.

programme.title: 10 Days Scotland
programme.desc: Robbie’s journey to reconnect with his Scottish roots begins in Edinburgh, the stunning capital city perched on extinct volcanoes. Navigating the twists of the Royal Mile, strutting around the majestic Edinburgh castle and learning to sip scotch like a true Scotsman, he feels a tad closer to his heritage. The real fun kicks in, however, when he stumbles onto a rather flamboyant way to unleash his inner Highlander.

programme.title: Xplore Bulgaria
programme.desc: Like Rome, Plovdiv straddles seven hills; but as Europe’s oldest continuously inhabited city, it’s far more ancient. As Catriona takes a tour of the city to see its iconic attractions such as a Roman Amphitheatre, which was once the setting for gladiator fights, and the striking Baroque Saints Constantine and Helena Church, she begins to see how seamlessly modern life blends with the age-old ruins. Along the way, she realizes why Plovdiv is called the ‘Eternal City’ of Bulgaria.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: The autumn of 2006 brings hurricanes to the North Atlantic and hot dry winds fan forest fires across Northern Ontario. Host/adventurer George Kourounis has traveled to some awesome hurricanes, including Rita and Katrina, with his pal Mark Robinson. This year they stormchase in Newfoundland, site of the hurricane that pulled Mark out of a life-threatening depression.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: The Angry Planet team heads to Africa to climb the steep and very active Nyiragongo Volcano in the Congo that erupted in 2002, sending 125,000 people fleeing for their lives. Host/adventurer George Kourounis explores the bubbling lake of molten lava and investigates the risk the dangerous volcano poses to both the people of city of Goma and the Mountain Gorillas who live on the nearby jungle slopes.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: The “Angry Planet” team hopes to film the natural wonders and extreme phenomena of this fascinating Central Asian country, including a spectacularly burning crater of natural gas, underground lakes, sandstorms and remnants of the dinosaurs.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: George tracks twisters through the Tornado Alley and descends into the Erte Ale Volcano.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: Host/adventurer George Kourounis explores the American Southwest during the Desert Monsoon. He ups the danger factor by traveling with wild atheist shock-jock R.J. Evans to track massive lightning storms which can produce bolts of up to one hundred million volts. The pair come close - too close - to dangerous electrical clouds swirling over Tucson, Sedona and Monument Valley.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: Host George Kourounis has braved many terrifying phenomena – but none as frightening as the one he takes on in this episode: marriage! To make sure his new bride is on the same adventurous page with him, he proposes to get married on the lip of an exploding volcano, on the South Pacific island of Tanna, in Vanuatu. Before the native preacher, dressed in grass skirt and kustom garb, gets to perform the smoky vows, George descends into the erupting volcano to bring out red hot samples of the lava it is producing.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: With summer wildfires overpowering the Yukon forests, host/adventurer George Kourounis follows the fabled route of the Klondike Gold Rush sourdoughs through the bawdy town of Skagway, Alaska, paddling the white water rivers and the White Horse Rapids into the Yukon. He travels on mountain bike, steam train and Cessna to experience the huge fires and meet the northern fire crews battling the blazes.

Her inner journey led her to discover a passion for naturopathy as she rediscovered her love for nature and learned the healing qualities of the plants around her. programme.title: Virginie (Lyon)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Virginie (Lyon)
programme.desc: Virginie’s beautiful handwritten lettering decorates the walls and windows of many shops in and around Lyon, France, as she lives out her passion of finding beauty in every stroke. A former waitress, Virginie was struggling to find her calling when she suffered a life-altering horse accident that almost left her handicapped. At only 30, she was forced to put her whole life into perspective. She finally found herself through a love for graphic design and lettering, combined with a desire for freedom that came with working independently. To motivate other women, she has also launched “Ladyboss”, a network of inspiring women entrepreneurs.

programme.title: Laetitia (French Alps)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Laetitia (French Alps)

Remembering the teachings of her grandmother, she began to venture outdoors into the surrounding Alps and study the different plants at her fingertips. Today she holds a wealth of knowledge about the medicinal and aromatherapeutic value of plants that she applies to making natural products. With utmost respect for the environment, Laetitia gathers only what she needs in order to make herbal infusions.

programme.title: Louise (Oleron Island)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Louise (Oleron Island)

Repurposing a camping car, she set up a brunch and tea-time spot where the guests can hand-pick their ingredients in the adjacent organic fields. Louise transforms the ingredients into favourite creations of hers and even joins her father for boat trips when she needs to stock up on fresh fish for the menu!

programme.title: Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 1

We head to Japan to talk about the impact of new technologies, then to the Republic of Congo in Bukavu for the coltan harvest. How does our total consumption affect the environment? What permanent brands are we imposing on our planet? How can we differentiate between useful and useless purchases?

programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Juliette (Morbihan)
programme.desc: Juliette has long been aware of the delicate beauty of nature. For years she spent her life on the sea, organising regattas for the traditional sailboats that are famous in the French region of Morbihan. Her appreciation for the elements made for a smooth transition as she decided to leave the water behind and return to the earth. Learning to shape a ball of clay into a graceful and elegant object, she discovered a passion for ceramics. Today, she lives from her creations and makes pieces that reflect their surroundings, the stunning Gulf of Morbihan.

programme.title: Anna (Brittany)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Anna (Brittany)
programme.desc: Anna’s unusual background provided inspiration for her life change. Her career began as a wolf trainer for cinema and it was during these years that she developed her deep love for animals. After being tired of seeing them used as props and constantly in cages, she decided to leave the world of show business behind and start an eco-friendly sheep and goat pasture. To further share her passion for these gentle animals, Anna has opened a conservatory farm where visitors can experience first-hand the joys of being close to nature. She also makes amazing goat cheese!

programme.title: Cristina (Spain)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Cristina (Spain)
programme.desc: At 31 years old, the last thing Cristina expected when she went to see the doctor about a blocked ear was to leave the consultation with a diagnosis for Breast Cancer. This young and passionate sociologist decided to apply the same philosophy to her treatment as she did when surfing: when a wave crashes down on you, get up and try again. Through her healing journey she deepened her love for the ocean and also discovered the therapeutic capabilities of yoga for cancer patients. Today she shares her practice through surf and yoga retreats and is specialised in oncological yoga, helping others heal.

programme.title: Idoia (Spain)

programme.desc: Idoia thrives on weaving together the sources of inspiration that surround her. Heavily influenced by the natural beauty of her home region of Galicia, Spain, she creates unique woven pieces from diverse and beautiful materials. Idoia’s pieces represent her vision of a modern woman, drawing from the traditions and experiences of those who perfected the craft before her and also pushing to innovate and adapt her creations for the modern world. Her recent collaboration with luxury fashion house Loewe is a dream come true for this modern artisan.

To tell the adventure of oil, Yann Arthus-Bertrand and his team went to the United States, the country which depends the most on black gold. programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 1 - Everything is living and everything is linked - Part 1
programme.desc: Through the most magnificent images and astonishing human stories, Man is at the heart of the biodiversity that he must respect and preserve. We find ourselves in Kenya, where the biodiversity is particularly rich, in the Massaï Mara reserve. Then, in the Democratic Republic of Congo, where the worrying disappearance of hippos from Lake Edward has unexpected consequences for the survival of fishermen. Then, in the sanctuary of life, the Pantanal region in Brazil, where millions of animal and plant species are teeming, some of the worlds great wetlands also in danger. In Tasmania, Yann Arthus-Bertrand fights against the napalm deforestation of one of the oldest and most beautiful forests...

programme.title: The flavors of flowers
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Julies Frenchy Cookbook - Season 4 - The flavors of flowers
programme.desc: Eating flowers might appear unconventional, but we often consume them without even realizing it. Consider artichokes, for instance : they are essentially large, unopened flowers. Capers are the preserved buds of flowers soaked in vinegar, and cloves are dried flower buds. We also find courgette flowers, saffron pistils, orange blossom water used to flavor pastries, and the violet sweets that evoke memories of our childhood. In addition to adding aesthetic appeal and providing a dose of vitamins to our plates, flowers elevate the flavors of a dish and can even serve as a vegetable substitute.

programme.title: Destination Okinawa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Blue Zones of Longevity - Season 1 - Destination Okinawa
programme.desc: Genetic, biological, cultural and dietary factors combine to make the Japanese island of Okinawa a zone of extreme longevity. Why is it that cancer is virtually non-existent here? Well see that the famous Japanese trio of "rice, fish and soy" is not the key to longevity, but a diet based on plants, lots of green leafy vegetables and endemic sweet potatoes. Self-restriction and strong social ties are other elements that our naturopathic chef and attending physician will discover on site, together with local inhabitants and scientists.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - USA: The end of oil - Part 2
programme.desc: "The end of oil" is the amazing story of a raw material which has revolutionized mans life in just a century. But today, oil reserves are depleting. In his crazy race for always more production, Man didnt manage to preserve this precious energy that took million years for the Earth to give out. To tell the adventure of oil, Yann Arthus-Bertrand and his team went to the United States, the country which depends the most on black gold. At the start of the 21st century, it is now urgent to realize that oil resources are limited. Its today that we have to act and get organized, in order to prepare the new era to come. While all our economies are based on the petrol barrels price, well...

programme.title: WOF 2024 #19: Pasko the Magic Move
programme.desc: Recovering from testicular cancer, professional athlete and filmmaker Maarten Molenaar embarks on a journey to Fuerteventura to learn a new freestyle windsurfing trick - the Pasko.

programme.title: WOF 2024 #13: GKA and GWA - Best Of World Cup Cape Verde
programme.desc: Cape Verde is blessed with a moderate climate, north-easterly trade winds and warm ocean swells that break on the islands reefs, making it a paradise for Kite-Surfing and wingfoiling. Sal island in particular boasts one of the worlds greatest right-hand point-breaks.

programme.title: Keep On Keeping On

programme.title: Marathon Internationale de Gorges de l´Ardeche and SainteLyon (FRA)
programme.desc: The Ardèche Gorges International Marathon is back, bringing together thousands of participants in this breathtaking setting. AND trail running The Saintelyon has developed into a real institution: 17,000 participants take part

programme.title: Expedition Antarctica - Caro North - Antarctic
programme.desc: Ice climbing, ski mountaineering and days of sailing on open waters through the infamous Drake Passage: 28-year-old extreme athlete Caro North set off for a four-week expedition to the far south of our continent.

programme.title: LAAX OPEN 2020 (SUI)
programme.desc: The 5th edition of the LAAX OPEN is taking place from January 13 to 18, 2020. It is the snowboarding event highlight in Europe’s mountains and guarantees snowboarding at its finest.

programme.title: Mammut Project 360 Grad
programme.desc: "Project360" takes digital mapping into the third dimension and makes the legendary Eiger North Face a virtual experience. A view through the eyes of the climber, directly from the wall. The impressive 360° panorama of the walls: www.project360.mammut.ch

programme.title: Roopkund - Mountainbike Expedition to the Indian Himalaya
programme.desc: Hans Rey, Richie Schley and Joscha Forstreuter travelled to the Indian Himalayas to the mysterious Roopkund Lake, which is known for having hundreds of ancient human skeletons lying dormant at its bottom. This is followed by a descent of 3,500 metres in altitude.

programme.title: Searching for the Rivergod II
programme.desc: The documentary "Searching for the River God - The Journey continues" shows in fantastic images extreme kayaking on the most attractive and remote rivers in the world in Siberia, the jungles of Mexico and in Iceland.

programme.title: adidas Sickline - Extreme Kayak World Championship - The Documentary
programme.desc: This is the documentary about the history of the famous "Wellerbrucke" rapids, a famous section of the glacier-fed Ötztaler Ache river in Tyrol, and the adidas Sickline Extreme Kayak World Championship.

programme.title: Cape Epic 2025 - Live delayed Part 1
